    "description": "准备好与生长在迈尔多中心的黑暗作斗争了吗？你认为你有足够的技能和勇气去战斗，将Maeldor从这一厄运中拯救出来吗？这片土地充满了危险、怪物、陷阱、宝藏和更多的东西!<br><br>跳入这个史诗般的故事，控制Maeldor的3个传奇英雄之一，Turmaeg、Thilberiel或Pelethorn，进行流畅而精确的战斗 一个巨大的世界，有很多背景故事，这些故事也可以在我们的网站上找到<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/1b5067c8fd10356c251b569692065e91.poster.avif?t=1744173637\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/1b5067c8fd10356c251b569692065e91.webm?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/1b5067c8fd10356c251b569692065e91.mp4?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>人物升级<br>积累你的技能和能力，变得更加强大，揭示传奇英雄的真正力量! Turmaeg被Kuuli女神亲自赐予了月之铠甲和剑，而Anoriel带着由Narinar森林中牢不可破的树木制成的传奇之弓 &quot;Tura&quot;，拥有 &quot;灵魂水召唤 &quot;能力的Pelethorn带着他的 &quot;水灵魂 &quot;旅行，以帮助他的旅程!  升级你的角色，揭开他们强大的力量，成为不可阻挡的力量!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/d0f0c19d80d28074ab75fcba63314c65.poster.avif?t=1744173637\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/d0f0c19d80d28074ab75fcba63314c65.webm?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/d0f0c19d80d28074ab75fcba63314c65.mp4?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不同的敌人<br>兽人、吸血鬼、海盗、死灵法师、龙和更多的人! 与黑暗的仆人战斗，用月亮的光芒征服他们!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/cafc98404579b6abc6f671b51691bf2f.poster.avif?t=1744173637\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/cafc98404579b6abc6f671b51691bf2f.webm?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/cafc98404579b6abc6f671b51691bf2f.mp4?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>厨师打架<br>Maeldor是一个危险的地方，让我向你保证! 8个具有独特战斗风格的传奇性终级BOSS! 如果你想继续你的旅程，你必须打败他们!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/073696f94606e52c3132ee6fcba18ea3.poster.avif?t=1744173637\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/073696f94606e52c3132ee6fcba18ea3.webm?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/073696f94606e52c3132ee6fcba18ea3.mp4?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>手工制作的世界<br>你在这个游戏中看到的一切都是手工制作的! 独特的关卡可供旅行和探索! 从茂密的绿色和金色森林到荒芜死寂的冰封之地，这个美丽的魔幻世界正等待着你的到来!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/0b944dbf1431c5a18c61b9c6497b3e94.poster.avif?t=1744173637\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/0b944dbf1431c5a18c61b9c6497b3e94.webm?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/0b944dbf1431c5a18c61b9c6497b3e94.mp4?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>寻找宝藏<br>探索巨大的关卡，选择不同的路径，并找到隐藏的宝藏! 揭开这个神奇领域的秘密吧!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/5bd177ccd40ff7fdbe26bbf22759fe82.poster.avif?t=1744173637\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/5bd177ccd40ff7fdbe26bbf22759fe82.webm?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/5bd177ccd40ff7fdbe26bbf22759fe82.mp4?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>独特的关卡<br>精心打造的关卡，具有独特的特点和环境，冰冷的地面，致命的陷阱，危险的山峰，神奇的平台，以及更多! 在你前进的过程中，通过改变机械和环境来保持参与!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/524f040b851309d4ccd87d5fac8a6538.poster.avif?t=1744173637\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/524f040b851309d4ccd87d5fac8a6538.webm?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230620/extras/524f040b851309d4ccd87d5fac8a6538.mp4?t=1744173637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一场伟大的冒险正摆在你面前，在巫师Aglaroth的指导下，你将猎杀怪物，与兽人国王作战，在海盗船上航行，成为一名猎人，发现隐藏的宝藏，并在这场拯救迈尔多的探险中挑战自我",
